  m_text: 'Hi Mr. Clarke,


    I forgot to send this to you earlier. This is the
    number to our support team if your lock breaks or needs repairing. The Engineer
    did tell me that there was a bug in the lock''s system, though I can''t really
    seem to be able to find it. Call me anyways and I''ll probably have it figured
    out. Also I think the code is 5 digits actually.


    Thanks,

    Daedalus
    Lockworks'
