  m_text: 'Hi Mr. Clarke,


    I believe that my colleague called you earlier. He
    told me that he forgot to mention that I had stopped by the other day and left
    a few tools in the room. Call me back if you would like to get started on the
    project and need help.


    Thank you,

    Samwell, Tartarus Contracting'
